    {
      "id": "73d86f45-6887-ef11-8474-000d3a37e3b6",
      "type": "GeneralText",
      "area": "General",
      "position": 3,
      "content": "- If possible, complete the 3 lower division courses (Anthro 1, 2, &amp; 3) at your transfer institutions. - Plan to complete any remaining prerequisites during your first semester at Berkeley. For more information on the major in Anthropology: Frances R. Bright Undergraduate Academic Advisor Department of Anthropology 215 Anthropology &amp; Art Practice Building University of California, Berkeley, CA 94720 f.bright@berkeley.edu , http://anthropology.berkeley.edu",
